Telkom Agrees to Increase Pay 7% This Year, 6.5% in 2012, Solidarity Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-09-12T10:07:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-12/telkom-agrees-to-increase-pay-7-this-year-6-5-in-2012-solidarity-says.html
Telkom South  Africa  Ltd.’s latest
pay offer has been accepted by the Solidarity labor union, the
workers’ group said.  Telkom, Africa’s largest fixed-line phone operator, will
increase pay 7 percent this year and 6.5 percent in 2012,
Solidarity said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  